  <brief_title>Postoperative Pulpal Complications in Posterior Resin Composite Restorations Without Glass-ionomer Cement Lining</brief_title>
  <official_title>A 2-year Clinical Study on Postoperative Pulpal Complications Arising From the Absence of a Glass-ionomer Lining in Deep Occlusal Resin Composite Restorations</official_title>
